                    "text": "An astradaemon bends light, appearing shifted from its true position, though still in the same space. Creatures targeting the astradaemon must attempt a DC 11 flat check, as if the astradaemon were hidden, even though it remains observed. Effects such as the Blind-Fight feat and halfling\u2019s keen eyes that apply on the flat check against hidden creatures also apply against a displaced astradaemon."
